This whole song is beyond the standard kpop. It's higher level of music which include powerful lyrics, angelic vocal, dynamic choreo, almost professional acting and dark, sad atmosphere.  I already watched this like hundred times but still I cannot stop myself form admiring every piece of this.
"100 ways" telling story of love which fell to the grave and broken soldier who tell us what he lost and what he learned from his experience. When we think about it as a story of simple man who don't want to give up on love it hits us different, stronger. And this man is legendary Jackson Wang. Not just kpop idol, but ARTIST.

snippet.textDisplay:
Shout out to the director which we unfortunately don"t know. Please, let's appreciate his and dancers effort in this video.
This play of lights are incredible! Once scenery is completely dark and later it's point directly at one person, so in this case Jackson and his lover, but between these scenes we can see light from behind a little higher than dancers. When the woman appear the light show up with her and behind the tree which give us an amazing view.
Don't forget that hands gestures also control the lights so from the beginning to the end of video we are witnesses of pure ART.
